{
  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "Based on the approach used by Saldana (2009), the research team read the survey answers to obtain a general sense of what participants were saying.",
    "We then divided the data into smaller samples of text and assigned codes or labels to them, similar to the approach used by Varpio et al. (2017).",
    "Then, our research team reviewed these sample texts and applied the codes we had created.",
    "Where codes did not match subsequent text samples, our team created additional codes.",
    "These codes were then clustered into broader categories as themes."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
